Subject: [PATCH AUTOSEL 5.7 04/28] riscv/atomic: Fix sign extension for RV64I
Date:   Tue, 23 Jun 2020 13:34:59 -0400
Message-Id: <20200623173523.1355411-4-sashal@kernel.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.25.1
